**jsp代码 **

**
**

1.  **<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" %>**
2.  **<html>**
3.  **  <head>**
4.  **    <title>$Title%sSourceCode%lt;/title>**
5.  **    <script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>**
6.  **    <script>**
7.  **      $(function(){**
8.  **        // 获取所有的省份信息**
9.  **        showArea(0,"#provience")**
10. **      })**
11. **      function showArea(val,selectID){**
12. **        $.ajax({**
13. **          type:"GET",**
14. **          url:"areaController.do",**
15. **          data:{parentID:val},**
16. **          dataType:"json",**
17. **          success:function(areas){**
18. **            // 清除上一次选择省份时,遗留的城市**
19. **            $(selectID).html('<option>-请选择-</option>');**
20. **            $.each(areas,function(i,e){**
21. **              $(selectID).append('<option
    value="'+e.areaid+'">'+e.areaname+'</option>')**
22. **            })**
23. **            if(selectID== "#city"){**
24. **              $("#qu").html('<option>-请选择-</option>');**
25. **            }**
26. **          }**
27. **        })**
28. **      }**
29. **    </script>**
30. **  </head>**
31. **  <body>**
32. **  籍贯:**
33. **  <select id="provience" onchange="showArea(this.value,'#city')">**
34. **    <option>-请选择-</option>**
35. **  </select>**
36. **  <select id="city" onchange="showArea(this.value,'#qu')">**
37. **    <option>-请选择-</option>**
38. **  </select>**
39. **  <select id="qu">**
40. **    <option>-请选择-</option>**
41. **  </select>**
42. **  </body>**
43. **</html>**

**AreaController代码 **

**
**

1.  **package com.msb.controller;**
2.  **import com.google.gson.Gson;**
3.  **import com.msb.dao.AreaDao;**
4.  **import com.msb.dao.impl.AreaDaoImpl;**
5.  **import com.msb.pojo.Area;**
6.  **import com.msb.service.AreaService;**
7.  **import com.msb.service.impl.AreaServiceImpl;**
8.  **import javax.servlet.ServletException;**
9.  **import javax.servlet.annotation.WebServlet;**
10. **import javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet;**
11. **import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;**
12. **import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;**
13. **import java.io.IOException;**
14. **import java.util.List;**
15. **/****
16. ** * @Author: Ma HaiYang**
17. ** * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001**
18. ** */**
19. **@WebServlet("/areaController.do")**
20. **public class AreaController extends HttpServlet {**
21. **    private AreaService areaService=new AreaServiceImpl();**
22. **    @Override**
23. **    protected void service(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse
    resp) throws ServletException, IOException {**
24. **        Integer parentID=0;**
25. **        try {**
26. **            parentID= Integer.parseInt(req.getParameter("parentID"));**
27. **        } catch (NumberFormatException e) {**
28. **            e.printStackTrace();**
29. **        }**
30. **        List<Area> areas=areaService.findByParentID(parentID);**
31. **        String json = new Gson().toJson(areas);**
32. **        resp.setCharacterEncoding("UTF-8");**
33. **        resp.setContentType("text/html;charset=UTF-8");**
34. **        resp.getWriter().print(json);**
35. **    }**
36. **}**

** **

**AreaService代码 **

**
**

1.  **package com.msb.service.impl;**
2.  **import com.msb.dao.AreaDao;**
3.  **import com.msb.dao.impl.AreaDaoImpl;**
4.  **import com.msb.pojo.Area;**
5.  **import com.msb.service.AreaService;**
6.  **import java.util.List;**
7.  **/****
8.  ** * @Author: Ma HaiYang**
9.  ** * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001**
10. ** */**
11. **public class AreaServiceImpl implements AreaService {**
12. **    private AreaDao areaDao =new AreaDaoImpl();**
13. **    @Override**
14. **    public List<Area> findByParentID(Integer parentID) {**
15. **        List<Area> areas = areaDao.findByParentID(parentID);**
16. **        return areas;**
17. **    }**
18. **}**

** **

**AreaDao代码 **

**
**

1.  **package com.msb.dao.impl;**
2.  **import com.msb.dao.AreaDao;**
3.  **import com.msb.dao.BaseDao;**
4.  **import com.msb.pojo.Area;**
5.  **import java.util.List;**
6.  **/****
7.  ** * @Author: Ma HaiYang**
8.  ** * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001**
9.  ** */**
10. **public class AreaDaoImpl extends BaseDao implements AreaDao  {**
11. **    @Override**
12. **    public List<Area> findByParentID(int parentID) {**
13. **        String sql="select * from area where parentid= ?";**
14. **        return baseQuery(Area.class, sql, parentID);**
15. **    }**
16. **}**
